0017FF  2               ;--------------------------------------------------------------
0017FF  2               ; catalog: Display disk directory in 5-column layout.
0017FF  2               ; Uses direct video writes so text memory is untouched.
0017FF  2               ; Paginates at 22 rows. Refresh restores editor on return.
0017FF  2               ;--------------------------------------------------------------
